# arcadedb-embedded

**⚠️ This is a placeholder release (v0.0.2) - DO NOT USE IN PRODUCTION**

This package is a placeholder for the `arcadedb-embedded` PyPI project namespace.

## Real Release

The actual production-ready releases start from version 25.10.1 and above.

Please install a recent version:

```bash
pip install arcadedb-embedded>=25.10.1
```

- **GitHub Repository**: https://github.com/humemai/arcadedb-embedded-python
- **Documentation**: https://humemai.github.io/arcadedb-embedded-python/
- **ArcadeDB Upstream**: https://github.com/ArcadeData/arcadedb

## About

ArcadeDB embedded multi-model database with bundled JRE - no Java installation required.

This placeholder version contains no functionality.
